  "title": "Locum/Perm Podiatrist (public healthcare, good career progression) #HCL",
  "description": "<p>Job Scope:</p><p>·        \nDiagnose and manage foot and lower limb\nconditions.</p><p>·        \nProvide treatment plans for issues such as foot\npain, diabetic foot care, and nail or skin conditions.</p><p>·        \nEducate patients on preventive foot care and\nproper footwear.</p><p>·        \nPerform minor surgical procedures where\nnecessary.</p><p>Requirements:</p><p>·        \nDegree in Podiatry or equivalent.</p><p>·        \nRegistered/licensed with the relevant health\nauthority.</p><p>·        \nGood manual dexterity and attention to detail.</p><p>·        \nStrong communication and patient education\nskills.</p><p>·        \nExperience with diabetic foot management is an\nadvantage.</p><p>If you are interested in any of the positions, do kindly\ndrop your most updated resume to kaileylee@recruitexpress.com.sg  </p><p>Kailey Lee Jia Yueh</p><p>EA Personnel No: R24126040</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifesciences\nDivision)</p><p>EA License: 99C4599</p>",
